Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:53.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾修顿…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.56,0:18:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.42,0:18:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的是妳…我一直在找妳
